446
00:32:15,131 --> 00:32:16,090
¿Te acuerdas?

447
00:32:18,175 --> 00:32:19,260
Dios, tenías...

448
00:32:25,599 --> 00:32:26,600
Si hago esto...

449
00:32:28,352 --> 00:32:30,438
